{"tid":1615440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[民調輸緊] (一齊bot加速)你認為香港應否就《反蒙面法》立法？","createTime":"2019-10-03T05:54:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T06:41:23.000Z","uid":128984,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b33770ddb8bdd7c2b3c7c69a0a9ee440c4d2526a","tid":1615440,"uid":128984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:54:18.000Z","msg":"見到有巴打話今日會有記招推禁蒙面法, <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>怪得之禽日突然間 Etnet 個投票對家加快左速度</strong></span>, <br />\n依家50萬人投左, 結果只係 49:51, 我整左個好水皮既 bot 出黎, 希望幫到下手<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xFSA54ieIX8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxFSA54ieIX8&d=2%2FeNT3TbtuwIHwt2a%2FmQGMdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=79900c4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xFSA54ieIX8</a><br />\n<br />\n要行 windows PC, 仲要裝一個 app 先, 同埋要用 firefox (唔好意思 咁多要求 真係唔係專業, 本身唔係 IT 人, 只希望砌磚引玉] <br />\n<br />\nbot 做法教學在此 (約要15-20分鐘設定, 之後可以約15秒可投票一次, 要手動入驗證碼)<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2o0jn1Z\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2o0jn1Z&d=2%2FeNT3TbtuwIHwt2a%2FmQGMdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=6b0d5615\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2o0jn1Z</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Source: <br />\n記招推禁蒙面法</strong></span><br />\n聽(今)日3點有班仆街想逼政府推禁蒙面法呀！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1613724\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1613724</a>"},{"pid":"3b37a12dcd0373161d01edb4126c8c0a2249028c","tid":1615440,"uid":229920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:54:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb33ec2a737990648c78dd604a25ae26df1a199e","tid":1615440,"uid":187950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:55:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1dc9de92d7c708e1c5c7e4b8b557fb248f0741eb","tid":1615440,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:55:43.000Z","msg":"[和理非入]只要有心 人人都係物資站，和理非係時候進化做輔助兵<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1615420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1615420</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5ab4b164135ceb0c530022e08e7b06d89ec5eef0","tid":1615440,"uid":170160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:57:34.000Z","msg":"外國已立幪面法國家，只係禁止遊行示威時幪面，平時一般生活時係毋須要實施。因為平時空氣質素差、傳染病流行季節、免疫能力低、長期病患者、及臉部有傷疤、或剛做完臉部手術等等...莫非平時都要禁止???"},{"pid":"99098856c0164cfe82fe6d7f2c67278cfcf8d277","tid":1615440,"uid":108347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:00:38.000Z","msg":"屌，佢過埋先好，快撚啲升級，根本而家係一定升級，你咁樣拖法仲多人受害，根本遲早都係要去到開大拖嘅地步<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你唔好再用保護和理非做藉口去打陣地戰<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1611719\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1611719</a>"},{"pid":"6a9fa1fabe3f5ede15cbd1e48a07e758c8d47c65","tid":1615440,"uid":264983,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:02:34.000Z","msg":"過由佢過，但民意唔牀輸比佢"},{"pid":"2d489bdbcc4d21ac7f57cb62ccd581a3aad75fc0","tid":1615440,"uid":264983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a9fa1fabe3f5ede15cbd1e48a07e758c8d47c65","tid":1615440,"uid":264983,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:02:34.000Z","msg":"過由佢過，但民意唔牀輸比佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:02:54.000Z","msg":"唔好"},{"pid":"b823e4732d470f161ad86c68b4bb9508b3e9108a","tid":1615440,"uid":128984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:19:32.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"85e66f8610e6e1af5b7ecaebd2635a59a0c298ec","tid":1615440,"uid":264983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:27:26.000Z","msg":"補番條投票 link<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/lifestyle/voting.php?catpage=1&amp;id=1228\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftc%2Flifestyle%2Fvoting.php%3Fcatpage%3D1%26id%3D1228&d=2%2FeNT3TbtuwIHwt2a%2FmQGMdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=07cf92db\" target=\"_blank\">http: